title: Daewoo Plastic Chrome Toaster, 2 Slice, Removable Crumb Tray, Browning Controls - Cream
features: BROWNING CONTROLS – Stop burning your toast and start making it to your perfection. Perfect for households who all have different preferred brownness, simply choose through the 6 browning settings and change the dial to best suit you

FUNCTIONS – Frozen bread, no problem you can now pop it in and choose to defrost or left it too long to butter and now it’s gone cold? You can place it back in and choose to reheat or simply cancel the toasting process when it suits you

EASY TO CLEAN AND STORE – Simply remove the crumb tray from the back of the toaster and empty into the bin after each use to stop the build-up of crumbs. Under the toaster you can wrap and store the cord to keep your sides free from mess and clutter

ELEGANT DESIGN – Plastic toaster featuring a chrome band is a timeless design that will match your kitchen even when you change up the design. Shop the full collection for a cohesive look and get your kettle to match, available in a range of colours

3 YEARS WARRANTY – Daewoo offers you 3 years warranty to ensure you are covered and to give you peace of mind. Are products are made to last but if you do come across any unforeseen issues you’re covered for 3 years, subject to online registration
